  "title": "Restaurant Service",
  "description": "<p><p><strong></strong></p><ul><li><p>Be the expert guide for our guests, ensuring smooth and attentive service from the moment they arrive until their goodbye.</p></li><li><p>Actively maintain a clean, organized, and vibrant atmosphere in the dining room.</p></li><li><p>Keep the team moving in harmony by restocking supplies and stepping in wherever help is needed.</p></li><li><p>Support and uplift fellow teammates, helping to foster our culture of energy and shared success.</p></li></ul><p><strong>You’re a Perfect Match If You:</strong></p><ul><li><p>Thrive in a fast-paced, people-focused environment.</p></li><li><p>Communicate clearly and connect effortlessly with guests and colleagues.</p></li><li><p>Take pride in all tasks, big and small, that make the restaurant shine.</p></li><li><p>Are a proactive problem-solver who loves to make things better.</p></li><li><p>Bring reliable, positive energy and believe in the power of teamwork.</p></li></ul><p><strong>What We Bring to the Table:</strong></p><ul><li><p>Competitive earnings with a great tip structure.</p></li><li><p>Flexible scheduling that respects your life outside of work.</p></li><li><p>A supportive, dynamic, and genuinely fun team.</p></li><li><p>Clear opportunities to grow your skills and advance your career here.</p></li><li><p>A complimentary employee meal every shift.</p></li></ul></p><p><br /></p><p><br /></p><p><br /></p><p>EA Personnel R22110043 Tan Eng Kang</p><p>EA License 21C0430 A Dreamworks Company Pte Ltd</p>",
